name: Interfering Dialogues 1
description: Harmonic dancing lines from modulated sine waves. The parameters for the curves are determined from a random seed, in this case the string "SHVEMBLDR", my friend who provided the tezos to mint my first NFT :-) The particular formulas to generate these curves are the result of my years long fascination and explorations into combinations of modulated sine waves.  Rendered as an SVG, it displays crisp at any resolution.  By Piter Pasma (https://piterpasma.nl and @piterpasma on Instagram)
